thread.title: Karen Foxton
thread.title_full: Liberty Flights reviewed by Karen Foxton

author: Karen Foxton
title: Karen Foxton
text: when i first used liberty flights i never in a million yrs really thought that it would work and that i could stop smoking as i have tried all the other methods , but 4yrs on and i have not had a cigarette or even wanted one , the products are brilliant , i got my sister to try aswell and she also has stopped smoking 21/2 yrs, i would recommend liberty flights to any one that really wants to become a non smoker .
